Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> command
Rule 1     command -> LOAD VECTOR
Rule 2     command -> SAVE VECTOR
Rule 3     command -> LOAD MODEL
Rule 4     command -> SAVE MODEL
Rule 5     command -> ANALYSE DATASET
Rule 6     command -> SAVE RESULTS
Rule 7     command -> sentiment
Rule 8     sentiment -> POSITIVE
Rule 9     sentiment -> NEGATIVE
Rule 10    sentiment -> NEUTRAL

Terminals, with rules where they appear

ANALYSE              : 5
DATASET              : 5
LOAD                 : 1 3
MODEL                : 3 4
NEGATIVE             : 9
NEUTRAL              : 10
POSITIVE             : 8
RESULTS              : 6
SAVE                 : 2 4 6
VECTOR               : 1 2
error                : 

Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

command              : 0
sentiment            : 7

Parsing method: LALR

